description:
Trump (1956-57) was Harvey Kurtzman’s dream magazine for Hugh Hefner and Playboy. Despite top talent (Mel Brooks, Will Elder, Jack Davis, Wally Wood), only two issues saw print. Six decades later the legendary Trump is finally collected, including the aborted issue #3. This overdue collection will blow comic fans’ minds!

Content that will rivet fans and collectors, including never-before-seen art intended for the unpublished Trump #3.

The fascinating creation of Trump magazine is detailed, featuring the unusual crossover of Hugh Hefner’s Playboy empire with the core team that created and then abandoned MAD magazine.
name: Volume Two: Trump: The Complete Collection

Deadpool and Ant-Man hit the beaches! But Deadpool's funny friends keep getting killed. The Marvel Murder Mystery continues!

From the Harley Quinn team of Jimmy Palmiotti & Justin Grey! The final blood-soaked chapter of Delete brings the most startling revelations yet as Spencer must face an army of trained killers to learn the truth about his painful past and how it ties to Senator Cox. This is also his one and only chance to give Kalina a chance at a normal life.

Any revolt begins with tears and finishes with blood.

Oösram was the most talented general of the fortress of Golgarsem, but he betrayed his Order and his King. On that day, he became nothing... His beard was cut, his properties were seized, his glory was forgotten...

He and his family are now Wanderers, working the earth, subjected to the whims of the powerful Dwarven Lords.

As time has passed, Oösram thinks he has renounced his former life, built a better one – but can he deny what he has always been?
name: Oösram of the Wanderers

description: Welcome to Skyrealm--where a thousand different cultures meet and all things are possible. Darius is a magic invoker of questionable prowess who's part of a trading party from the distant Unbroken Empire. But when the Unbroken transport is blasted out of the sky by pirates, Darius and his single surviving shipmate, Captain Krieger, find themselves up to their necks in trouble. Can they stay alive long enough to become the Heroes of Skyrealm? Discover a world of adventure that goes even further in Heroes of Skyrealm, mobile coming soon from Mechanist Games for iOS and Android!

Batman forms an alliance with the savage Hawkman, who is still determined to remove Batman and Batgirl hatch a plot to break into Cyborg’s database and get their hands on footage of Superman’s many executions. Their goal is to broadcast it to the world, and turn everyone against the regime. Meanwhile, an enraged and kryptonite-armed Hawkman finally has his confrontation with the Man of Steel!
